snippet.title: Cocoto Kart Racer GameCube Gameplay HD
snippet.description:
Cocoto Kart Racer GameCube Gameplay HD.

Cocoto Kart Racer is a 2005 racing video game developed by and released by Neko Entertainment for PlayStation 2, GameCube, Nintendo DS, Game Boy Advance, Microsoft Windows, Wii, iPhone and iPod Touch.
